      h2#endconcat End Concatenation

      p This is a small trick to prevent the last line of a paragraph from containing only one word.

      p So instead of:

      pre lorem ipsum dolor sit
        | amet

      p End concatenation produces:

      pre lorem ipsum dolor
        | sit amet

      p To use, simply add the class 
        code .s-endconcat
        |  or use the jQuery plugin

      pre $(element).s_endconcat()

      p Where 
        code element
        |  is the element to have enconcatenation applied

